            <span class="dw-work-tag">PORTFOLIO · IDENTITY · MOTION</span>
            <h3 class="dw-work-title">THE ARTIFACT</h3>
            <p class="dw-work-desc">Clinical terminal aesthetic applied to personal branding. Custom design system: 18 color tokens, 3 typefaces, 15 motion primitives.</p>
            <div class="dw-work-stack">
              <span>Astro</span><span>GSAP</span><span>Tailwind v4</span><span>React Islands</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Archon Interface -->
        <div class="dw-work-item">
          <div class="dw-work-img dw-work-img-archon">
            <div class="dw-work-img-content">
              <span class="dw-work-img-label">AGENT DASHBOARD</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dw-work-meta">
            <span class="dw-work-tag">DASHBOARD · DATA VIZ</span>
            <h3 class="dw-work-title">ARCHON INTERFACE</h3>
            <p class="dw-work-desc">Visual dashboard for AI agent orchestration. Real-time skill topology and execution graphs.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Aether Nexus -->
        <div class="dw-work-item">
          <div class="dw-work-img dw-work-img-aether">
            <div class="dw-work-img-content">
              <span class="dw-work-img-label">MULTI-AGENT UX</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dw-work-meta">
            <span class="dw-work-tag">UX SYSTEMS · INTERACTION</span>
            <h3 class="dw-work-title">AETHER NEXUS</h3>
            <p class="dw-work-desc">Interaction model for autonomous multi-agent coordination. Human-in-the-loop UX for self-correcting workflows.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS SECTION -->
  <section class="dw-section dw-section-alt" id="dw-process">
    <div class="dw-section-inner">
      <div class="dw-section-header">
        <span class="dw-section-num">02 //</span>
        <h2 class="dw-section-title">HOW I DESIGN</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="dw-process-steps">
        <div class="dw-step">
          <div class="dw-step-num">01</div>
          <h3 class="dw-step-title">DISCOVER</h3>
          <p class="dw-step-desc">User research, competitive audit, and constraint mapping before a single pixel moves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="dw-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="dw-step">
          <div class="dw-step-num" style="color:#EC4899;border-color:rgba(236,72,153,0.3)">02</div>
          <h3 class="dw-step-title">DEFINE</h3>
          <p class="dw-step-desc">Design tokens, interaction vocabulary, and system architecture before visual explorations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="dw-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="dw-step">
          <div class="dw-step-num" style="color:#FBBF24;border-color:rgba(251,191,36,0.3)">03</div>
          <h3 class="dw-step-title">CRAFT</h3>
          <p class="dw-step-desc">High-fidelity design with motion specs, edge cases, and developer handoff documentation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="dw-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="dw-step">
          <div class="dw-step-num" style="color:#4ADE80;border-color:rgba(74,222,128,0.3)">04</div>
          <h3 class="dw-step-title">SHIP</h3>
          <p class="dw-step-desc">I implement my own designs. Code-first verification that the vision survives production.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT SECTION -->
  <section class="dw-section" id="dw-contact">
    <div class="dw-section-inner dw-contact-inner">
      <h2 class="dw-contact-title">THE WORK RUNS<br/><em>WITHOUT ME.</em></h2>
      <p class="dw-contact-body">Until you need someone to build the next system. Open to design-engineering roles where architecture and aesthetic aren't separate conversations.</p>
      <a href="mailto:tahaa755@gmail.com" class="dw-contact-cta">
        OPEN A LINE
        <span>→</span>
      </a>
      <div class="dw-contact-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/SufficientDaikon" target="_blank">GITHUB</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ahmed-taha225" target="_blank">LINKEDIN</a>
        <a href="mailto:tahaa755@gmail.com">EMAIL</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style>
/* ====== DESIGN WORLD (Kore universe node) ====== */
.world-overlay {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  overflow-y: auto;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  will-change: transform;
}

/* ====== WORLD NAV ====== */
.world-nav {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 10;
  height: 52px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 2rem;
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
}
.design-nav {
  background: rgba(7,5,15,0.85);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(192,132,252,0.15);
}
.world-back-btn {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  background: transparent;
  border: 1px solid rgba(192,132,252,0.25);
  padding: 5px 12px;
  cursor: crosshair;
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(192,132,252,0.7);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}
.world-back-btn:hover { color: #C084FC; border-color: rgba(192,132,252,0.5); background: rgba(192,132,252,0.08); }
.world-nav-id {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}
.world-nav-num {
  font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: rgba(192,132,252,0.4);
}
.world-nav-label {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(192,132,252,0.7);
}
.world-nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
}
.world-nav-links a {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
  font-size: 8px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.2s ease;
}
.world-nav-links a:hover { color: #C084FC; }

/* ====== DESIGN HERO ====== */
.dw-hero {
  min-height: calc(100vh - 52px);
  background: #07050F;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
  gap: 4rem;
}
@media (min-width: 1024px) { .dw-hero { padding: 5rem 5rem 4rem; } }

.dw-hero-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.dw-hero-bg::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(192,132,252,0.18) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 32px 32px;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.dw-hero-img {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  opacity: 0.12;
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
}
.dw-orb {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(80px);
  animation: dw-float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.dw-orb-1 {
  width: 500px; height: 500px;
  top: -150px; left: -100px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124,58,237,0.35), transparent 70%);
  animation-delay: 0s;
}
.dw-orb-2 {
  width: 400px; height: 400px;
  bottom: -100px; right: -80px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(236,72,153,0.3), transparent 70%);
  animation-delay: 3s;
}
.dw-orb-3 {
  width: 300px; height: 300px;
  top: 40%; left: 45%;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(192,132,252,0.2), transparent 70%);
  animation-delay: 6s;
}
@keyframes dw-float {
  0%,100% { transform: translate(0,0) scale(1); }
  50% { transform: translate(20px,-20px) scale(1.1); }
}
.dw-hero-noise {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
  opacity: 0.04;
  mix-blend-mode: overlay;
}

/* Hero content */
.dw-hero-left {
  flex: 1;
  max-width: 600px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}
.dw-hero-right {
  flex: 0 0 360px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  display: none;
}
@media (min-width: 1100px) { .dw-hero-right { display: block; } }

.dw-overline {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.dw-overline-num {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(192,132,252,0.7);
}
.dw-overline-dash {
  flex: 1;
  max-width: 60px;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(192,132,252,0.5), transparent);
}

.dw-hero-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Manrope', serif;
  font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.0;
  color: #F8F4FF;
  margin: 0 0 1.8rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.05em;
}
.dw-title-line { display: block; }
.dw-title-line em {
  font-style: italic;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C084FC 0%, #EC4899 50%, #FBBF24 100%);
